# VHS tape — regenerate with: vhs assets/authority.tape
Output assets/authority.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 38ms
Set Padding 12

Type "# AI ranks entities, not pages. How deep is your topical authority?"
Sleep 1.5s
Enter
Type "geo authority --sitemap https://geoready.dev/sitemap.xml --brand GeoReady"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 12s
Sleep 3s
